description: It is sad when a man cannot take care of himself. I am a compassionate guy but sometimes enough is enough. This young man had a gambling problem. He gambled away all his money in an online casino. When his girlfriend found out about his problem, she gave him one last chance and started watching closely what he paid for. To continue his hobby, he borrowed money. I guess he expected to finally hit that fat juicy jackpot. Instead, he ended up 30 000 in debt. Being caught between his angry girlfriend and the angry loan-shark he had a very difficult choice to make. He didn´t want to live on his own, nor to end up being crippled. So he chose my dick to get him out of this mess.
title: Debt Dandy 142
